          "notes": "Module excels at concept accuracy, narrative framing, and quiz quality. Real case studies (Mata v. Avianca, Bing Chat, BloombergGPT) ground abstract problems in concrete failures. Critical weakness: Labs are conversational AI tutor interactions with no verifiable hands-on execution—learners cannot actually build, test, or debug a RAG system, leaving the capability delta unclear and unmeasurable.",
